headline: Wall Street Analysts See a 28.68% Upside in West Pharmaceutical (WST): Can the Stock Really Move This High?
summary: The mean of analysts' price targets for West Pharmaceutical (WST) points to a 28.7% upside in the stock. While this highly sought-after metric has not proven reasonably effective, strong agreement among analysts in raising earnings estimates does indicate an upside in the stock.
